</ul>
<p>Every month the Kardashian Clothing line is expanding.  Soon, with the launch of ShopDASHOnline - You will finally be able to order Kardashian Clothing direct from DASH via the internet.  Until then there are several options for 2012 and beyond.  The styles As Seen On the Kardashians are a nice selection of apparel and accessories offered by Singer 22.  These fashions are true Kardashian style as seen in the pictures.  Boutique2You also has some nice items seen on the Kardashian sisters.  



